cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.SY, cs.NI, cs.DC 

The paper deals with decision making in multi-agent systems, which is a core topic in artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.AI is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses game theory and equilibrium analysis, which are important topics in cs.GT (Game Theory and Economics) and cs.SY (Systems and Control). The paper also deals with load balancing in network problems, which falls under cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing).
